issue.title: Refactor the survey into a single module.
issue.body:
This allows the survey to take advantage of a UI flag to indicate whether it's editing or not.
Handling deltas and controlling the inputs on a stateful array of questions is painful.
Managing this with redux is also... very painful.
We can take advantage of Formik to do this for us.

I'll temporarily keep a demo live here: http://macmaster.gq
